name: Eyemaster
details:
HM2-style distortionEYEMASTER was specifically designed to channel the Swedish death metal tone, endearingly nicknamed the "Swedish buzzsaw". As that term implies, EYEMASTER is not a subtle overdrive.
It is not transparent and it does not "sit well in a mix". Rather, it burns an unholy path straight through the mix.
•    Aggressive death metal distortion
•    All-analog circuitry
•    True Bypass
